title: Lavrov, OSCE Head Confirm Call for Increase of Observers' Number in Ukraine
text: Russian Foreign Minister Sergei Lavrov and Organization for Security and Co-operation in Europe (OSCE) Secretary General Lamberto Zannier confirmed Monday their mutual interest in increasing the number of OSCE monitors in Ukraine to 1,000. ...
